<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color:#ABB2CB;
            color: #0a3d6a;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
            padding-top: 20px;
            color: #777777;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Hi!</h1>
    <p>Please confirm your email address by clicking the following link:</p>
    <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{ signedUrl|raw }}" class="btn">Confirm my Email</a>
    </p>
    <p>This link will expire in 1 hour.</p>
    <p>Cheers!</p>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you did not request this email, please ignore it.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
